Jenette Goldstein https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jenette_Goldstein 0 Jenette Elise Goldstein (born February 4, 1960) is an American actress, best known for her Saturn Award–winning role as Private Vasquez in the 1986 science fiction action film Aliens.
